LogFile.FinalText: Impressing, how similar they look. That is how many people think of the two princesses of Denmark. There are many similarities between Mary and Marie, but as many, if not more differences. They are both from abroad, from non-royal families and have both found a prince of Denmark - Mary is married to Crown Prince Frederik, whereas Marie is married to Prince Joachim. The names and the looks are incredibly similar. Both are beautyful like models with their long, dark hair and big, brown eyes. But despite the long list of similarities, Mary and Marie are also two individuals, who have lived and still do live their lives their own way, and therefore with individual values and characters.
